{
  "stem": "15694.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that is also why I wrote the book, because any time I wanted to sp-- speak, I could not stick to a subject, always veering away into another vision.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Oh, I have to tell you that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have to tell you that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then I couldn't find my way back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But since I had written the book, that's how I can-- that's why I can tell, more or less, the story straight, really only a little bit.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, we left everything except the one postcard which I had for my mother, with a scribble-- with a message in the back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I tore the edges to a minimum, so I can still have the writing and the picture, and to fit into my palm.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I went through the door, somebody said, what have you got there?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it was only-- you could see a picture.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "An inmate, and he smiled-- smiled politely, nicely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only later I wondered what this man must have seen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we went into the gas chambers, but not knowing it-- on-- hoping it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we were, of course, like everybody else, told that's the shower room, the bathroom, shower room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So heavy doors closed behind us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I looked up and I saw shower hoses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the water came, hope-- life and hope came back to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even only very young people can do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I kept to myself what I really wanted to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hello, daddy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Complain.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The water's not very warm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that's sort of a show-- a show of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we had water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then we were led out at the opposite side.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
